  13 Jan 2008; William L. Thomson Jr. <wltjr@gentoo.org>
  +files/cpuid-fomit-frame-pointer-b23.patch,
  +files/external-giflib-b23.patch, +files/external-jpeg-splash-b23.patch,
  +files/external-libpng-b23.patch, +files/external-zlib-b23.patch,
  +files/external-zlib-splash-b23.patch,
  +files/fontconfig-directlink-b23.patch,
  +files/gettimeofday-declaration-b23.patch, +files/jdk-cxxflags-b23.patch,
  +files/tempname-free-b23.patch, +openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha23.ebuild:
  Bumped to b23, couldn't find b24 source. Migrated all patches, dropped a few
  that no longer apply. Dropped all keywords since it does not merge. Needs
  work on binary plugins, etc so it will merge. Will resume work later, or
  anyone else can resume in the mean time

